#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:70
msgid ""
"The routes are grouped by purpose below. The operational surface (health,"
" status, cache and storage control) lives at top-level paths; routes "
"inherited from the shared ``internal_api_server`` package keep their "
"original paths for compatibility with the vLLM-embedded API server."
msgstr "下面的路由按目的分组。操作接口（健康检查、状态、缓存和存储控制）位于顶层路径；从共享的 ``internal_api_server`` 包继承的路由保持其原始路径，以与嵌入的 vLLM API 服务器兼容。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:77
msgid ""
"Several handlers report failure in the response **body** rather than via "
"a non-200 status code (e.g. ``DELETE /l2`` returns ``200`` with "
"``ok=false``, and ``/periodic-threads-health`` returns ``200`` with "
"``healthy=false``). The error-field name is also not uniform: "
"``/healthcheck`` and ``/clear-cache`` use ``reason`` on failure, while "
"``/status``, ``/conf``, and ``/kvcache/check`` use ``error``. Per-"
"endpoint details below are authoritative."
msgstr "多个处理程序在响应的 **body** 中报告失败，而不是通过非 200 状态码（例如，``DELETE /l2`` 返回 ``200`` 和 ``ok=false``，而 ``/periodic-threads-health`` 返回 ``200`` 和 ``healthy=false``）。错误字段名称也不统一：``/healthcheck`` 和 ``/clear-cache`` 在失败时使用 ``reason``，而 ``/status``、``/conf`` 和 ``/kvcache/check`` 使用 ``error``。每个端点的详细信息如下是权威的。"

