#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:336
msgid ""
"Returns a detailed snapshot of the MP engine's internal state. The "
"payload is assembled by ``MPCacheServer.report_status()``: a fixed set of"
" engine-level fields, the full storage-manager status, plus whatever keys"
" each loaded module contributes (so the exact key set depends on which "
"modules are active — ``registered_gpu_ids`` / ``cache_context_meta`` come"
" from the transfer module, ``active_prefetch_jobs`` from the lookup "
"module, and blend modes add their own fields). Intended for operators and"
" debugging, not for monitoring (use Prometheus metrics for time-series "
"data — see :doc:`observability/index`)."
msgstr "返回 MP 引擎内部状态的详细快照。有效负载由 ``MPCacheServer.report_status()`` 组装：一组固定的引擎级字段、完整的存储管理器状态，以及每个加载模块贡献的键（因此确切的键集取决于哪些模块处于活动状态 — ``registered_gpu_ids`` / ``cache_context_meta`` 来自传输模块，``active_prefetch_jobs`` 来自查找模块，混合模式添加它们自己的字段）。旨在供操作员和调试使用，而非监控（使用 Prometheus 指标获取时间序列数据 — 参见 :doc:`observability/index`）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:391
msgid ""
"**Response** (``503 Service Unavailable``) when the engine has not yet "
"been initialized:"
msgstr "**响应** (``503 服务不可用``) 当引擎尚未初始化时："

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:407
msgid "``GET /conf``"
msgstr "``GET /conf``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:409
msgid ""
"Returns every server-side configuration object registered on "
"``app.state.configs`` (typically ``mp``, ``storage_manager`` and "
"``observability``) as a single indented JSON document. Dataclasses are "
"serialized via ``safe_asdict``; other values go through "
"``make_json_safe``. Useful for confirming what the process actually "
"loaded — including environment overrides — without restarting."
msgstr ""
"返回在 ``app.state.configs`` 上注册的每个服务器端配置对象（通常是 ``mp``、``storage_manager`` 和"
" ``observability``），作为一个单一的缩进 JSON 文档。数据类通过 ``safe_asdict`` 序列化；其他值通过 "
"``make_json_safe`` 处理。对于确认进程实际加载的内容（包括环境覆盖）非常有用，而无需重启。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:434
msgid ""
"**Response** (``503 Service Unavailable``) when configs are not wired "
"onto ``app.state`` yet:"
msgstr "**响应**（``503 服务不可用``），当配置尚未连接到 ``app.state`` 时："

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:450
msgid "``GET /version``, ``GET /lmc_version``, ``GET /commit_id``"
msgstr "``GET /version``, ``GET /lmc_version``, ``GET /commit_id``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:452
msgid "Version descriptors. Each returns a bare JSON **string** (not an object):"
msgstr "版本描述符。每个返回一个裸 JSON **字符串**（而不是对象）："

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:454
msgid ""
"``GET /version`` — the combined descriptor from "
"``lmcache.utils.get_version()``, formatted ``\"<version>-<commit_id>\"`` "
"(e.g. ``\"0.3.1-ca79ea33\"``). On a source checkout without build-time "
"version metadata, each missing component falls back to the literal "
"``\"NA\"`` (so a metadata-less build returns ``\"NA-NA\"``)."
msgstr "``GET /version`` — 来自 ``lmcache.utils.get_version()`` 的组合描述符，格式为 ``\\\"<version>-<commit_id>\\\"``（例如 ``\\\"0.3.1-ca79ea33\\\"``）。在没有构建时版本元数据的源代码检出中，每个缺失的组件将回退为字面值 ``\\\"NA\\\"``（因此没有元数据的构建返回 ``\\\"NA-NA\\\"``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:459
msgid ""
"``GET /lmc_version`` — the raw package version string "
"(``lmcache.utils.VERSION``); empty string ``\"\"`` when the generated "
"``lmcache._version`` module is absent."
msgstr "``GET /lmc_version`` — 原始包版本字符串 (``lmcache.utils.VERSION``)；当生成的 ``lmcache._version`` 模块缺失时返回空字符串 ``\\\"\\\"``。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:462
msgid ""
"``GET /commit_id`` — the git commit id baked into the build "
"(``lmcache.utils.COMMIT_ID``); empty string ``\"\"`` when unavailable."
msgstr "``GET /commit_id`` — 构建中嵌入的 git 提交 ID (``lmcache.utils.COMMIT_ID``)；当不可用时为空字符串 ``\\\"\\\"``。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:465
msgid "All three are unconditional ``200 OK``."
msgstr "这三者都是无条件的 ``200 OK``。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:467 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1110
msgid "**Examples:**"
msgstr "**示例：**"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:476
msgid "Cache Control"
msgstr "缓存控制"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:479
msgid "``POST /clear-cache``"
msgstr "``POST /clear-cache``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:481
msgid ""
"Force-clears **all** KV cache data currently held in L1 (CPU) memory "
"(delegates to the ``ManagementModule``)."
msgstr "强制清除当前保存在 L1 (CPU) 内存中的 **所有** KV Cache 数据（委托给 ``ManagementModule``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:486
msgid ""
"This endpoint is destructive and bypasses read/write locks. In-flight "
"store or prefetch operations may be corrupted. Use only when the server "
"is idle, or when recovering from a known-bad cache state."
msgstr "此端点是破坏性的，并绕过读/写锁。正在进行的存储或预取操作可能会被损坏。仅在服务器空闲时或从已知的坏缓存状态恢复时使用。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:490
msgid "The request body is ignored."
msgstr "请求体将被忽略。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:516
msgid "``GET /kvcache/check``"
msgstr "``GET /kvcache/check``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:518
msgid ""
"Compute MD5 checksums over the engine KV cache, grouped ``chunk_size`` "
"blocks per hashed chunk. MP mode addresses KV storage by block IDs "
"natively (the same units used by ``STORE`` / ``RETRIEVE``), so the "
"endpoint is fully block-centric: ``block_ids`` enumerates the target "
"blocks and ``chunk_size`` counts blocks per chunk. Intended for "
"diagnostics and round-trip integrity checks from ``lmcache bench server``"
" — not for the inference data path."
msgstr "计算引擎 KV Cache 的 MD5 校验和，按每个哈希块的 ``chunk_size`` 块进行分组。MP 模式原生地通过块 ID 访问 KV 存储（与 ``STORE`` / ``RETRIEVE`` 使用的单位相同），因此该端点完全以块为中心：``block_ids`` 列举目标块，``chunk_size`` 计算每个块的块数。旨在用于诊断和从 ``lmcache bench server`` 进行往返完整性检查——而不是用于推理数据路径。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:526 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:663
#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:744
msgid "**Query parameters:**"
msgstr "**查询参数：**"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:532 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:669
#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:750
msgid "Name"
msgstr "名称"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:533
msgid "Required"
msgstr "必需的"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:535
msgid "``block_ids``"
msgstr "``block_ids``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:536 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:539
msgid "yes"
msgstr "是"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:537
msgid "Engine block IDs in mixed format, e.g. ``\"0,[2,5],8\"``."
msgstr "混合格式的引擎块 ID，例如 ``\"0,[2,5],8\"``。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:538
msgid "``chunk_size``"
msgstr "``chunk_size``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:540
msgid "Positive integer — number of blocks per hashed chunk."
msgstr "正整数 — 每个哈希块的块数。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:541
msgid "``instance_id``"
msgstr "``instance_id``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:542
msgid "no (default ``0``)"
msgstr "否（默认 ``0``）"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:543
msgid "Registered KV context ID on the engine."
msgstr "引擎上注册的 KV 上下文 ID。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:544
msgid "``layerwise``"
msgstr "``layerwise``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:545
msgid "no (default ``false``)"
msgstr "不（默认 ``false``）"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:546
msgid ""
"If ``true``, return per-layer checksums keyed by ``\"layer_<idx>\"``; "
"otherwise a single aggregated digest per chunk over all layers."
msgstr "如果为 ``true``，则返回按 ``\"layer_<idx>\"`` 键入的逐层校验和；否则返回每个块的所有层的单个聚合摘要。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:562
msgid ""
"When ``layerwise=true``, ``chunk_checksums`` is a dict keyed by "
"``\"layer_<idx>\"`` whose values are per-layer lists."
msgstr ""
"当 ``layerwise=true`` 时，``chunk_checksums`` 是一个以 ``\"layer_<idx>\"`` "
"为键的字典，其值是逐层列表。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:565 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:643
#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:715 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:799
#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1034 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1304
msgid "**HTTP status codes:**"
msgstr "**HTTP 状态码:**"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:567 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:801
msgid "``200``: success."
msgstr "``200``: 成功。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:568
msgid ""
"``400``: ``block_ids`` missing/malformed, or ``chunk_size`` missing or "
"non-positive."
msgstr "``400``: ``block_ids`` 缺失/格式错误，或 ``chunk_size`` 缺失或非正数。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:570
msgid ""
"``404``: ``instance_id`` not registered, or the registered KV tensors are"
" empty."
msgstr "``404``: ``instance_id`` 未注册，或者注册的 KV 张量为空。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:572
msgid ""
"``501``: engine has no ``cache_contexts``, or the KV format is not "
"supported by this endpoint (page-buffer-fused and cross-layer layouts are"
" declined until a real need appears)."
msgstr "``501``: 引擎没有 ``cache_contexts``，或者该端点不支持 KV 格式（页面缓冲融合和跨层布局在真正需要之前被拒绝）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:575
msgid "``503``: engine not yet initialized on ``app.state``."
msgstr "``503``: 引擎尚未在 ``app.state`` 上初始化。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:588
msgid "L2 Storage Management"
msgstr "L2 存储管理"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:590
msgid ""
"Three endpoints — ``GET /l2/adapters``, ``DELETE /l2``, and ``GET "
"/l2/keys`` — let operators enumerate the configured L2 backends, purge "
"keys from one, and enumerate what is currently resident."
msgstr "三个端点 — ``GET /l2/adapters``、``DELETE /l2`` 和 ``GET /l2/keys`` — 允许操作员枚举配置的 L2 后端，从一个后端清除键，并枚举当前驻留的内容。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:595
msgid ""
"``DELETE /l2`` and ``GET /l2/keys`` accept an optional "
"``?adapter=<type_name>`` query parameter to target a specific adapter. "
"Omit the selector to target the **primary** (first-configured) adapter — "
"the v1 behavior, preserved for clients that don't care about multi-"
"adapter deployments. When multiple adapters share a ``type_name``, the "
"first match wins. Use ``GET /l2/adapters`` to learn the valid selectors."
msgstr "``DELETE /l2`` 和 ``GET /l2/keys`` 接受一个可选的 ``?adapter=<type_name>`` 查询参数，以针对特定的适配器。省略选择器以针对 **主**（第一个配置的）适配器——这是 v1 行为，为不关心多适配器部署的客户端保留。当多个适配器共享一个 ``type_name`` 时，第一个匹配的适配器将被选中。使用 ``GET /l2/adapters`` 来了解有效的选择器。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:603
msgid ""
"All three are intended for operator / admin workflows (\"purge this "
"user's keys\", \"show me what's resident\", \"garbage-collect orphans "
"after a rename\"). They are **not** on the inference data path."
msgstr "这三者旨在用于操作员/管理员工作流程（“清除该用户的密钥”、“显示我所拥有的内容”、“在重命名后收集孤儿”）。它们**不**在推理数据路径上。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:607
msgid ""
"L1 is intentionally not touched. Keys deleted from L2 may still return "
"from L1 until the L1 eviction controller expires them naturally; callers "
"that need an L1+L2 purge should layer their own L1 invalidation or wait "
"for natural L1 eviction."
msgstr "L1 被故意不触及。从 L2 删除的键可能仍会从 L1 返回，直到 L1 逐出控制器自然过期；需要 L1+L2 清除的调用者应该自行分层 L1 失效或等待自然 L1 逐出。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:612
msgid ""
"The coordinator's eviction loop uses ``DELETE /l2`` automatically (see "
":doc:`coordinator` — \"L2 usage tracking and eviction\"); the ``GET "
"/l2/keys`` endpoint also powers the coordinator's startup resync. Manual "
"``curl`` usage is reserved for ad-hoc operator actions and debugging."
msgstr "协调器的逐出循环自动使用 ``DELETE /l2``（参见 :doc:`coordinator` — “L2 使用跟踪和逐出”）；``GET /l2/keys`` 端点也为协调器的启动重新同步提供支持。手动使用 ``curl`` 保留给临时操作员操作和调试。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:618
msgid ""
"For full request/response semantics, pagination, error codes, and the "
"event flow back to the coordinator, see the design doc at "
"``docs/design/v1/multiprocess/l2_apis.md``."
msgstr "有关完整的请求/响应语义、分页、错误代码以及事件流回协调器的信息，请参阅设计文档 ``docs/design/v1/multiprocess/l2_apis.md``。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:623
msgid "``GET /l2/adapters``"
msgstr "``GET /l2/adapters``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:625
msgid "Enumerate every L2 adapter the engine has loaded, in configuration order."
msgstr "列出引擎已加载的每个 L2 适配器，按配置顺序排列。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:639
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"``primary`` is ``true`` only on the first entry. An engine that has no L2"
" backends returns ``{\"adapters\": []}`` (still ``200`` — the engine is "
"initialized, it just has no L2 storage)."
msgstr "``primary`` 仅在第一个条目上为 ``true``。没有 L2 后端的引擎返回 ``{\\\"adapters\\\": []}``（仍然是 ``200`` — 引擎已初始化，只是没有 L2 存储）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:645
msgid "``200``: success (including the no-adapters case)."
msgstr "``200``: 成功（包括无适配器的情况）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:646 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1042
msgid "``503``: engine not initialized."
msgstr "``503``: 引擎未初始化。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:655
msgid "``DELETE /l2``"
msgstr "``DELETE /l2``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:657
msgid ""
"Delete a caller-supplied list of keys from one L2 adapter. Idempotent: "
"keys absent from the adapter are skipped silently; keys currently locked "
"by in-flight store/load tasks are skipped so the delete never corrupts an"
" active transfer. The blocking adapter call is run off the event loop."
msgstr "从一个 L2 适配器中删除调用者提供的键列表。幂等性：适配器中缺失的键会被静默跳过；当前被进行中的存储/加载任务锁定的键会被跳过，以确保删除操作不会破坏正在进行的传输。阻塞适配器调用在事件循环之外运行。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:672 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:753
msgid "``adapter``"
msgstr "``adapter``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:673 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:754
msgid "primary"
msgstr "主适配器"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:674 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:755
msgid ""
"``type_name`` of the target adapter (see ``GET /l2/adapters``). Omit to "
"target the primary (first-configured) adapter. First match wins when "
"multiple adapters share a ``type_name``."
msgstr "目标适配器的 ``type_name``（见 ``GET /l2/adapters``）。省略以目标为主适配器（第一个配置的适配器）。当多个适配器共享同一 ``type_name`` 时，优先匹配第一个。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:678
msgid ""
"Per-key successful deletions fire ``on_l2_keys_deleted`` on the adapter's"
" listeners — when the coordinator is wired (see ``--coordinator-l2-event-"
"reporting``), the deletions show up at the coordinator's ``POST "
"/l2/events`` as ``\"type\": \"delete\"`` events. The coordinator's "
"eviction + usage trackers learn about the deletion from that event flow, "
"not from the response of this call."
msgstr "每个键成功删除时会在适配器的监听器上触发 ``on_l2_keys_deleted`` — 当协调器已连接时（参见 ``--coordinator-l2-event-reporting``），删除操作会以 ``\"type\": \"delete\"`` 事件的形式出现在协调器的 ``POST /l2/events`` 中。协调器的逐出和使用跟踪器通过该事件流了解删除情况，而不是通过此调用的响应。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:685
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**Body:** ``{\"keys\": [EncodedObjectKey, ...]}`` where each "
"``EncodedObjectKey`` is"
msgstr "**主体:** ``{\\\"keys\\\": [EncodedObjectKey, ...]}`` 其中每个 ``EncodedObjectKey`` 是"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:698
msgid ""
"``object_group_id`` (default ``0``) and ``cache_salt`` (default ``\"\"``)"
" are optional for backward compatibility with older wire payloads. The "
"batch is capped at ``10000`` keys per request."
msgstr "``object_group_id``（默认 ``0``）和 ``cache_salt``（默认 ``\"\"``）是为了与旧的 wire 负载保持向后兼容而可选的。每个请求的批量限制为 ``10000`` 个键。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:712
msgid ""
"On adapter-level failure the response is still ``200`` with ``ok=false`` "
"and an ``error`` field carrying the reason."
msgstr "在适配器级别失败时，响应仍然是 ``200``，并且 ``ok=false``，同时 ``error`` 字段包含原因。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:717
msgid "``200``: request reached the adapter (check ``ok`` for outcome)."
msgstr "``200``: 请求已到达适配器（检查 ``ok`` 以获取结果）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:718
msgid ""
"``400``: batch exceeds the limit, or a key payload violates an "
"``ObjectKey`` invariant (bad hex, ``@`` in ``model_name``, forbidden "
"``cache_salt`` character)."
msgstr "``400``: 批量超出限制，或者一个键负载违反了 ``ObjectKey`` 不变式（错误的十六进制，``model_name`` 中的 ``@``，禁止的 ``cache_salt`` 字符）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:721 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:803
msgid "``404``: ``?adapter=<name>`` does not match any configured adapter."
msgstr "``404``: ``?adapter=<name>`` 与任何已配置的适配器不匹配。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:722
msgid ""
"``422``: Pydantic-level body-shape failure (missing ``keys``, wrong field"
" types)."
msgstr "``422``: Pydantic 级别的主体形状失败（缺少 ``keys``，字段类型错误）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:724 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:808
msgid "``503``: engine not initialized, or no L2 adapters configured."
msgstr "``503``: 引擎未初始化，或未配置 L2 适配器。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:740
msgid "``GET /l2/keys``"
msgstr "``GET /l2/keys``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:742
msgid "Paginate keys currently resident in one L2 adapter."
msgstr "分页当前驻留在一个 L2 适配器中的键。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:758
msgid "``model_name``"
msgstr "``model_name``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:759 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:766
msgid "none"
msgstr "无"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:760
msgid "Restrict the result to keys whose ``model_name`` matches."
msgstr "将结果限制为与 ``model_name`` 匹配的键。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:761
msgid "``page_size``"
msgstr "``page_size``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:762
msgid "``500``"
msgstr "``500``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:763
msgid ""
"Max entries per page. Must be in ``[1, 5000]``; an out-of-range value is "
"rejected with ``422`` (it is not silently clamped)."
msgstr "每页最大条目数。必须在 ``[1, 5000]`` 范围内；超出范围的值将被拒绝并返回 ``422``（不会被静默限制）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:765
msgid "``page_token``"
msgstr "``page_token``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:767
msgid ""
"Opaque cursor from the previous page's ``next_page_token``. Omit on the "
"first call; pass back verbatim on subsequent calls."
msgstr "来自上一页的 ``next_page_token`` 的不透明游标。在第一次调用时省略；在后续调用中逐字传回。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:770
msgid ""
"The page token is private to the adapter; do not parse or modify it. "
"Adapters that support listing (currently only the S3 adapter via "
"``ListObjectsV2``) guarantee best-effort consistency, not snapshot "
"isolation — concurrent stores or deletes during a paginated walk may "
"cause keys to appear, disappear, or shift between pages."
msgstr "页面令牌是适配器私有的；请勿解析或修改它。支持列出功能的适配器（目前仅通过 ``ListObjectsV2`` 的 S3 适配器）保证尽力而为的一致性，而不是快照隔离——在分页遍历期间的并发存储或删除可能导致键出现、消失或在页面之间移动。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:797
msgid "``next_page_token`` is ``null`` when the listing is exhausted."
msgstr "``next_page_token`` 在列出内容耗尽时为 ``null``。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:802
msgid "``400``: malformed ``page_token`` (adapter-level)."
msgstr "``400``: 错误的 ``page_token``（适配器级别）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:804
msgid "``422``: ``page_size`` outside ``[1, 5000]``."
msgstr "``422``: ``page_size`` 超出 ``[1, 5000]`` 范围。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:805
msgid ""
"``501``: selected adapter does not implement listing. In v1 only "
"``S3L2Adapter`` does; adapters wrapped by ``SerdeL2AdapterWrapper`` "
"inherit the wrapped adapter's behavior."
msgstr "``501``: 选定的适配器不支持列出。在 v1 中，只有 ``S3L2Adapter`` 支持；由 ``SerdeL2AdapterWrapper`` 包装的适配器继承被包装适配器的行为。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:810
msgid "**Example:** paginate every key for a model."
msgstr "**示例：** 为模型分页每个键。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:825
msgid "Quota Management"
msgstr "配额管理"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:827
msgid ""
"These endpoints manage the per-``cache_salt`` storage budgets consumed by"
" the ``IsolatedLRU`` eviction policy (selected via ``--eviction-policy "
"IsolatedLRU``). Quotas are **soft**: setting a limit does not reject "
"writes — any over-budget ``cache_salt`` is evicted at the next eviction "
"cycle (~1 s). A ``cache_salt`` with no registered quota has an effective "
"limit of ``0`` bytes, so its data is cleared next cycle (allowlist "
"semantics)."
msgstr ""
"这些端点管理由 ``IsolatedLRU`` 逐出策略（通过 ``--eviction-policy IsolatedLRU`` "
"选择）消耗的每个 ``cache_salt`` 存储预算。配额是 **软性** 的：设置限制并不会拒绝写入 — 任何超出预算的 "
"``cache_salt`` 会在下一个逐出周期（约 1 秒）被逐出。没有注册配额的 ``cache_salt`` 有一个有效限制为 ``0`` "
"字节，因此其数据将在下一个周期被清除（白名单语义）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:835
msgid ""
"These endpoints are no-ops on engines that did not start with "
"``--eviction-policy IsolatedLRU``: the ``QuotaManager`` is still present,"
" but the LRU policy ignores the registered quotas."
msgstr ""
"这些端点在未使用 ``--eviction-policy IsolatedLRU`` 启动的引擎上是无操作的：``QuotaManager`` "
"仍然存在，但 LRU 策略会忽略注册的配额。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:839
msgid ""
"**URL escaping for the empty salt.** ``cache_salt=\"\"`` (un-salted / "
"anonymous traffic) cannot appear in a URL path parameter, so the API "
"accepts the sentinel ``_default`` in its place. ``PUT /quota/_default`` "
"sets the quota for ``cache_salt=\"\"``, and ``_default`` is echoed back "
"in responses for the empty salt. A user that legitimately stores data "
"with ``cache_salt=\"_default\"`` cannot be managed via this HTTP API "
"distinctly from anonymous traffic — both map to the same path parameter; "
"pick any other value (e.g. ``\"default\"``) to disambiguate."
msgstr "**空盐的 URL 转义。** ``cache_salt=\\\"\\\"``（无盐/匿名流量）不能出现在 URL 路径参数中，因此 API 接受哨兵 ``_default`` 作为替代。``PUT /quota/_default`` 设置 ``cache_salt=\\\"\\\"`` 的配额，``_default`` 在空盐的响应中被回显。合法存储数据的用户 ``cache_salt=\\\"_default\\\"`` 不能通过此 HTTP API 与匿名流量区分管理——两者映射到相同的路径参数；选择任何其他值（例如 ``\\\"default\\\"``）以消除歧义。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:849
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``PUT /quota/{cache_salt}``"
msgstr "``PUT /quota/{cache_salt}``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:851
msgid "Create or update a quota."
msgstr "创建或更新配额。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:853
#, python-brace-format
msgid "**Body:** ``{\"limit_gb\": <float>}`` (required, finite, non-negative)."
msgstr "**主体:** ``{\\\"limit_gb\\\": <float>}`` （必需，有限，非负）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:861
msgid ""
"**Errors:** ``400`` for malformed JSON, missing ``limit_gb``, non-numeric"
" ``limit_gb``, ``nan`` / ``inf``, or negative values; ``503`` if the "
"engine is not initialized."
msgstr ""
"**错误:** ``400`` 表示 JSON 格式错误、缺少 ``limit_gb``、``limit_gb`` 不是数字、``nan`` / "
"``inf`` 或负值；``503`` 表示引擎未初始化。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:874
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``GET /quota/{cache_salt}``"
msgstr "``GET /quota/{cache_salt}``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:876
msgid "Read the current quota and live usage for one ``cache_salt``."
msgstr "读取当前配额和一个 ``cache_salt`` 的实时使用情况。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:889
msgid ""
"``exists`` is ``false`` when no quota was ever registered for this "
"``cache_salt`` (``limit_gb`` is then ``0.0`` and ``current_usage_gb`` "
"reflects whatever bytes are currently cached for that salt — those bytes "
"will evict next cycle under ``IsolatedLRU``). This endpoint never returns"
" ``404`` for an unknown salt."
msgstr "``exists`` 为 ``false`` 当这个 ``cache_salt`` 从未注册过配额时（``limit_gb`` 此时为 ``0.0``，而 ``current_usage_gb`` 反映当前为该盐缓存的字节数——这些字节将在下一个周期下逐出 ``IsolatedLRU``）。这个端点对于未知的盐永远不会返回 ``404``。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:896
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``DELETE /quota/{cache_salt}``"
msgstr "``DELETE /quota/{cache_salt}``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:898
msgid ""
"Remove a ``cache_salt``'s quota entry. Any bytes still cached under this "
"``cache_salt`` become over-budget on the next eviction cycle (effective "
"limit drops to ``0``) and will be evicted."
msgstr ""
"删除 ``cache_salt`` 的配额条目。任何仍然缓存于此 ``cache_salt`` 下的字节将在下一个逐出周期中超出预算（有效限制降至"
" ``0``），并将被逐出。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:908
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"When no quota was registered for the given ``cache_salt``, the response "
"is ``{\"cache_salt\": \"...\", \"status\": \"not_found\"}`` (still ``200 "
"OK``)."
msgstr ""
"当给定的 ``cache_salt`` 没有注册配额时，响应为 ``{\\\"cache_salt\\\": \\\"...\\\", "
"\\\"status\\\": \\\"not_found\\\"}``（仍然是 ``200 OK``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:912
msgid "``GET /quota``"
msgstr "``GET /quota``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:914
msgid "List every registered quota alongside its live usage."
msgstr "列出每个注册的配额及其实时使用情况。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:927
msgid ""
"Only ``cache_salt`` values with a **registered** quota appear; the empty "
"salt is reported under the ``_default`` key."
msgstr "只有带有 **注册** 配额的 ``cache_salt`` 值会出现；空盐会在 ``_default`` 键下报告。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:933
msgid "Runtime L2 Reconfiguration"
msgstr "运行时 L2 重新配置"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:935
msgid ""
"These endpoints are available when the server has a runtime-"
"reconfigurable L2 adapter. They only change LMCache runtime mappings and "
"metadata; backend resources such as DAX device paths must already exist "
"and be readable and writable by the server. The endpoint routes "
"``backend``, ``operation``, and the JSON request body into the generic L2"
" adapter reconfiguration API, while backend-specific validation and "
"migration semantics stay inside the adapter."
msgstr ""
"这些端点在服务器具有可运行时重新配置的 L2 适配器时可用。它们仅更改 LMCache 的运行时映射和元数据；后端资源如 DAX "
"设备路径必须已经存在，并且服务器必须能够读取和写入。该端点将 ``backend``、``operation`` 和 JSON 请求体路由到通用 "
"L2 适配器重新配置 API，而后端特定的验证和迁移语义则保留在适配器内部。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:942
msgid ""
"``backend`` and ``operation`` path segments are normalized (stripped and "
"lower-cased). Within a request body, ``adapter_index`` (default ``0``) is"
" **backend-local** — it indexes only the adapters of that backend, not "
"the engine-wide adapter list. If an L2 adapter is wrapped by serde, the "
"backend string is still the configured L2 adapter type, not the serde "
"wrapper type."
msgstr "``backend`` 和 ``operation`` 路径段被规范化（去除空格并转为小写）。在请求体内，``adapter_index``（默认为 ``0``）是 **后端本地** 的——它仅索引该后端的适配器，而不是整个引擎的适配器列表。如果 L2 适配器被序列化/反序列化包装，后端字符串仍然是配置的 L2 适配器类型，而不是序列化/反序列化包装类型。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:949
msgid "``GET /reconfigure/backends``"
msgstr "``GET /reconfigure/backends``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:951
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"List the backend strings that can be used in "
"``/reconfigure/{backend}/status`` and "
"``/reconfigure/{backend}/{operation}``."
msgstr "列出可以在 ``/reconfigure/{backend}/status`` 和 ``/reconfigure/{backend}/{operation}`` 中使用的后端字符串。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:965
msgid ""
"``enabled`` is ``false`` (and ``backends`` empty) when no reconfigurable "
"adapter is present."
msgstr "``enabled`` 为 ``false``（且 ``backends`` 为空）时表示没有可重新配置的适配器。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:968
msgid ""
"**HTTP status codes:** ``200`` on success; ``503`` if the engine is not "
"initialized."
msgstr "**HTTP 状态码：** ``200`` 表示成功；``503`` 表示引擎未初始化。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:972
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``GET /reconfigure/{backend}/status``"
msgstr "``GET /reconfigure/{backend}/status``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:974
msgid ""
"Report the runtime-manageable adapters for one backend type. Each adapter"
" entry's ``adapter_index`` is rewritten to its **backend-local** 0-based "
"index (the value to pass back in operation request bodies)."
msgstr "报告一个后端类型的运行时可管理适配器。每个适配器条目的 ``adapter_index`` 被重写为其 **后端本地** 的 0 基索引（在操作请求体中传回的值）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:991
msgid ""
"An unknown or empty backend returns ``enabled=false``, "
"``num_adapters=0``, ``adapters=[]`` (it is **not** a ``404``)."
msgstr "一个未知或空的后端返回 ``enabled=false``，``num_adapters=0``，``adapters=[]``（这**不是** ``404``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:994
msgid ""
"**HTTP status codes:** ``200`` on success; ``400`` if ``backend`` is "
"empty; ``503`` if the engine is not initialized."
msgstr "**HTTP 状态码:** ``200`` 表示成功；``400`` 如果 ``backend`` 为空；``503`` 如果引擎未初始化。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:998
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``POST /reconfigure/{backend}/{operation}``"
msgstr "``POST /reconfigure/{backend}/{operation}``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1000
msgid ""
"Apply one reconfiguration operation to a backend adapter. The request "
"body is a JSON object whose accepted fields depend on the backend and "
"operation. The ``200`` response is whatever the storage manager's "
"``reconfigure_l2_adapter`` returns (a backend-defined dict)."
msgstr "将一个重新配置操作应用于后端适配器。请求体是一个 JSON 对象，其接受的字段取决于后端和操作。``200`` 响应是存储管理器的 ``reconfigure_l2_adapter`` 返回的内容（一个后端定义的字典）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1005
msgid ""
"For the **generic** path (any backend other than ``dax``), the body "
"carries ``adapter_index`` plus any backend-specific fields, which are "
"forwarded verbatim to the adapter."
msgstr "对于 **通用** 路径（任何后端除了 ``dax``），请求体包含 ``adapter_index`` 以及任何特定于后端的字段，这些字段会逐字转发给适配器。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1009
msgid ""
"For **Device-DAX** (``backend=dax``), JSON request bodies are used "
"because DAX paths contain slashes. The accepted operations and fields "
"are:"
msgstr "对于 **Device-DAX** (``backend=dax``)，使用 JSON 请求体，因为 DAX 路径包含斜杠。接受的操作和字段包括："

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1016
msgid "Operation"
msgstr "操作"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1017
msgid "Body fields"
msgstr "主体字段"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1018
msgid "``add``"
msgstr "``add``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1019
msgid ""
"``device_path`` (str, required), ``size`` (int byte count or string such "
"as ``\"100GiB\"``, required), ``adapter_index`` (default ``0``)."
msgstr "``device_path``（str，必填），``size``（字节数或字符串，例如``\"100GiB\"``，必填），``adapter_index``（默认``0``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1021
msgid "``remove``"
msgstr "``remove``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1022
msgid ""
"``device_path`` (str, required), ``mode`` (``migrate`` | ``evict`` | "
"``drain``, default ``migrate``), ``force`` (bool, default ``false``), "
"``adapter_index`` (default ``0``)."
msgstr "``device_path`` (str, 必需), ``mode`` (``migrate`` | ``evict`` | ``drain``, 默认 ``migrate``), ``force`` (bool, 默认 ``false``), ``adapter_index`` (默认 ``0``)。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1025
msgid "``resize``"
msgstr "``resize``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1026
msgid ""
"``device_path`` (str, required), ``size`` (int or string, required), "
"``mode`` (``migrate`` | ``evict``, default ``migrate``), ``force`` (bool,"
" default ``false``), ``adapter_index`` (default ``0``)."
msgstr "``device_path``（str，必需），``size``（int 或 string，必需），``mode``（``migrate`` | ``evict``，默认 ``migrate``），``force``（bool，默认 ``false``），``adapter_index``（默认 ``0``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1030
msgid ""
"``size`` accepts an integer byte count or a string with a base-1024 unit "
"suffix (``b``, ``kib``, ``mib``, ``gib``, ``tib`` and the "
"``k``/``m``/``g``/``t`` aliases), e.g. ``\"100GiB\"``; it must resolve to"
" a positive value."
msgstr "``size`` 接受一个整数字节数或带有基于 1024 的单位后缀的字符串（``b``、``kib``、``mib``、``gib``、``tib`` 及其 ``k``/``m``/``g``/``t`` 别名），例如 ``\"100GiB\"``；它必须解析为一个正值。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1036
msgid "``200``: success (body is the storage manager's reconfigure result)."
msgstr "``200``: 成功（主体是存储管理器的重新配置结果）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1037
msgid ""
"``400``: empty ``backend``/``operation``, an unsupported DAX operation, "
"or an invalid ``size``."
msgstr "``400``: 空的 ``backend``/``operation``，不支持的 DAX 操作，或无效的 ``size``。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1039
msgid "``404``: ``adapter_index`` is out of range for the backend."
msgstr "``404``: ``adapter_index`` 超出后端范围。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1040
msgid ""
"``422``: request body fails validation (e.g. a missing required field, or"
" an unknown field in a DAX body — DAX bodies reject extras)."
msgstr "``422``: 请求体验证失败（例如，缺少必填字段或 DAX 请求体中的未知字段——DAX 请求体会拒绝额外字段）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1044
msgid ""
"See :doc:`/kv_cache/storage_backends/dax` for detailed request examples, "
"mode semantics, and validation guidance."
msgstr "有关详细的请求示例、模式语义和验证指导，请参阅 :doc:`/kv_cache/storage_backends/dax`。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1048
msgid "Observability"
msgstr "可观察性"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1051
msgid "``GET /metrics``"
msgstr "``GET /metrics``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1053
msgid ""
"Prometheus exposition format for every metric registered on the default "
"``prometheus_client`` registry (``Content-Type: text/plain``). Scrape "
"this directly from Prometheus. See :doc:`observability/index` for the "
"list of exported metrics."
msgstr "默认 ``prometheus_client`` 注册表中注册的每个指标的 Prometheus 展示格式 (``Content-Type: text/plain``)。直接从 Prometheus 抓取此数据。有关导出指标的列表，请参见 :doc:`observability/index`。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1065
msgid "``POST /metrics/reset``"
msgstr "``POST /metrics/reset``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1067
msgid ""
"Resets all LMCache observability metrics to their initial state "
"(``reset_observability_metrics``). Intended for test harnesses and "
"benchmarks — not for production."
msgstr ""
"重置所有 LMCache "
"可观察性指标到其初始状态（``reset_observability_metrics``）。旨在用于测试工具和基准测试——不适用于生产环境。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1071
msgid "**Response** (``200 OK``, ``text/plain``):"
msgstr "**响应**（``200 OK``, ``text/plain``）："

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1084
msgid "Diagnostics and Debugging"
msgstr "诊断与调试"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1087
msgid "``GET /loglevel``"
msgstr "``GET /loglevel``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1089
msgid ""
"Inspect or mutate Python logger levels at runtime. All responses are "
"``text/plain``. The endpoint has three modes driven by query parameters:"
msgstr "在运行时检查或修改 Python 日志记录器级别。所有响应都是 ``text/plain``。该端点有三种模式，由查询参数驱动："

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1096 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1134
#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1164
msgid "Query"
msgstr "查询"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1097 ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1135
#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1165
msgid "Behavior"
msgstr "行为"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1098
msgid "(no params)"
msgstr "(无参数)"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1099
msgid "List every logger registered with :mod:`logging` and its level."
msgstr "列出所有在 :mod:`logging` 中注册的记录器及其级别。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1100
msgid "``?logger_name=<name>``"
msgstr "``?logger_name=<name>``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1101
msgid "Return the effective level of the named logger."
msgstr "返回指定记录器的有效级别。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1102
msgid "``?logger_name=<name>&level=<LEVEL>``"
msgstr "``?logger_name=<name>&level=<LEVEL>``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1103
msgid ""
"Set the named logger (and its handlers) to ``LEVEL`` "
"(``DEBUG``/``INFO``/``WARNING``/``ERROR``/``CRITICAL``; case-"
"insensitive). Returns ``400`` on an unknown level."
msgstr "将命名的日志记录器（及其处理程序）设置为 ``LEVEL``（``DEBUG``/``INFO``/``WARNING``/``ERROR``/``CRITICAL``；不区分大小写）。如果级别未知，则返回 ``400``。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1107
msgid ""
"Passing ``level`` without ``logger_name`` matches none of the modes and "
"returns ``200`` with a ``null`` body."
msgstr "传递 ``level`` 而不带 ``logger_name`` 不匹配任何模式，并返回 ``200`` 和一个 ``null`` 响应体。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1124
msgid "``GET /threads``"
msgstr "``GET /threads``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1126
msgid ""
"Enumerate active Python threads in the server process along with their "
"stack traces, plus a total-count summary (``Content-Type: text/plain``). "
"Useful for live debugging of hangs or runaway workers."
msgstr "列出服务器进程中活动的 Python 线程及其堆栈跟踪，并提供总计摘要（``Content-Type: text/plain``）。对于实时调试挂起或失控的工作线程非常有用。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1136
msgid "``?name=<substr>``"
msgstr "``?name=<substr>``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1137
msgid "Keep only threads whose name contains ``<substr>`` (case-insensitive)."
msgstr "仅保留名称包含 ``<substr>`` 的线程（不区分大小写）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1139
msgid "``?thread_id=<int>``"
msgstr "``?thread_id=<int>``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1140
msgid "Keep only the thread with the matching ``ident``."
msgstr "只保留与匹配的 ``ident`` 相关的线程。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1144
msgid ""
"The response contains live stack traces and can disclose internal code "
"paths and state. Restrict network access to this endpoint in production."
msgstr "响应包含实时堆栈跟踪，并可能泄露内部代码路径和状态。在生产环境中限制对该端点的网络访问。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1154
msgid "``GET /periodic-threads``"
msgstr "``GET /periodic-threads``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1156
msgid ""
"Returns a JSON snapshot of the "
":class:`~lmcache.v1.periodic_thread.PeriodicThreadRegistry`: counts by "
"level plus per-thread status (last run timestamp, latest summary, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"返回 :class:`~lmcache.v1.periodic_thread.PeriodicThreadRegistry` 的 JSON "
"快照：按级别统计以及每个线程的状态（上次运行时间戳、最新摘要等）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1166
msgid "``?level=critical|high|medium|low``"
msgstr "``?level=critical|high|medium|low``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1167
msgid "Only include threads at the given level. ``400`` on unknown."
msgstr "仅包含给定级别的线程。对未知情况返回 ``400``。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1168
msgid "``?running_only=true``"
msgstr "``?running_only=true``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1169
msgid "Only include threads currently running."
msgstr "仅包含当前正在运行的线程。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1170
msgid "``?active_only=true``"
msgstr "``?active_only=true``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1171
msgid "Only include threads considered active (recent tick)."
msgstr "仅包括被视为活动的线程（最近的滴答）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1212
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``GET /periodic-threads/{thread_name}``"
msgstr "``GET /periodic-threads/{thread_name}``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1214
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Detailed status for a single periodic thread (the same per-thread object "
"shown in the ``threads`` list above). Returns ``404`` with ``{\"error\": "
"\"Thread not found: <name>\"}`` if the name is unknown."
msgstr "单个周期线程的详细状态（与上面的 ``threads`` 列表中显示的每个线程对象相同）。如果名称未知，则返回 ``404`` 和 ``{\\\"error\\\": \\\"Thread not found: <name>\\\"}``。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1225
msgid "``GET /periodic-threads-health``"
msgstr "``GET /periodic-threads-health``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1227
msgid ""
"Fast health check covering only ``critical`` and ``high`` level periodic "
"threads. A thread is flagged unhealthy when it is marked running but has "
"not ticked within its expected interval. Always returns ``200`` — health "
"is conveyed by the ``healthy`` boolean, not the HTTP status."
msgstr "快速健康检查，仅涵盖 ``critical`` 和 ``high`` 级别的周期性线程。当线程被标记为运行但在预期间隔内未进行计时时，它会被标记为不健康。始终返回 ``200`` — 健康状态通过 ``healthy`` 布尔值传达，而不是通过 HTTP 状态。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1242
msgid "When something is lagging:"
msgstr "当某些东西滞后时："

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1266
msgid "``GET /env``"
msgstr "``GET /env``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1268
msgid ""
"Dumps the process environment variables as a sorted, pretty-printed JSON "
"document. The response ``Content-Type`` is ``text/plain`` so it can be "
"piped directly to a terminal."
msgstr "将进程环境变量转储为排序后的美观打印 JSON 文档。响应的 ``Content-Type`` 为 ``text/plain``，因此可以直接通过管道传输到终端。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1274
msgid ""
"The payload contains **every** environment variable, including any "
"secrets injected via the environment. There is no redaction or auth — "
"restrict network access to this endpoint in production."
msgstr "有效负载包含 **每个** 环境变量，包括通过环境注入的任何秘密。没有任何编辑或身份验证 — 在生产环境中限制对该端点的网络访问。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1285
msgid "``POST /run_script``"
msgstr "``POST /run_script``"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1287
msgid ""
"Execute an uploaded Python script inside the server process. The script "
"is uploaded as multipart form data under the field name ``script`` and is"
" ``exec``'d with a restricted ``__builtins__`` (only ``print``, ``str``, "
"``int``, ``float``, ``list``, ``dict``, ``tuple``, ``set``, and a guarded"
" ``__import__``). Only modules listed in ``--script-allowed-imports`` can"
" be imported; the running FastAPI ``app`` is injected into the script "
"globals. If the script assigns a variable named ``result``, its "
"stringified value is returned; otherwise the body is ``\"Script executed "
"successfully\"`` (``Content-Type: text/plain``)."
msgstr "在服务器进程中执行上传的 Python 脚本。脚本作为多部分表单数据上传，字段名称为 ``script``，并在受限的 ``__builtins__`` 下被 ``exec`` 执行（仅允许 ``print``、``str``、``int``、``float``、``list``、``dict``、``tuple``、``set`` 和受保护的 ``__import__``）。仅允许导入在 ``--script-allowed-imports`` 中列出的模块；运行的 FastAPI ``app`` 会注入到脚本的全局变量中。如果脚本赋值给名为 ``result`` 的变量，则返回其字符串化值；否则返回正文为 ``\"脚本成功执行\"``（``Content-Type: text/plain``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1299
msgid ""
"This endpoint runs caller-supplied code in-process. The restricted "
"builtins are **not** a security sandbox — combined with the injected "
"``app`` object and any allowed imports, treat it as full remote code "
"execution. Never expose it on an untrusted network."
msgstr "此端点在进程中运行调用者提供的代码。受限的内置函数**不是**安全沙箱——结合注入的``app``对象和任何允许的导入，将其视为完全的远程代码执行。切勿在不受信任的网络上公开它。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1306
msgid "``200``: script executed."
msgstr "``200``: 脚本已执行。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1307
msgid "``400``: no ``script`` file provided."
msgstr "``400``: 未提供 ``script`` 文件。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1308
msgid ""
"``500``: an exception was raised during import setup or execution (body: "
"``\"Error executing script: <reason>\"``)."
msgstr "``500``: 在导入设置或执行期间引发了异常（主体：``\"执行脚本时出错：<reason>\"``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1319
msgid "Adding New Endpoints"
msgstr "添加新端点"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1321
msgid ""
"Endpoints are auto-discovered from "
"``lmcache/v1/multiprocess/http_apis/``. To add a new MP-only endpoint:"
msgstr "端点会从 ``lmcache/v1/multiprocess/http_apis/`` 自动发现。要添加一个新的仅限 MP 的端点："

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1324
msgid "Create a new module in that directory named ``<name>_api.py``."
msgstr "在该目录中创建一个名为 ``<name>_api.py`` 的新模块。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1325
msgid "Define a module-level ``router = APIRouter()``."
msgstr "定义一个模块级的 ``router = APIRouter()``。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1326
msgid "Register handlers on ``router`` using FastAPI decorators."
msgstr "使用 FastAPI 装饰器在 ``router`` 上注册处理程序。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1327
msgid ""
"Access the engine via ``request.app.state.engine`` and guard for the "
"``None`` case (engine not yet initialized)."
msgstr "通过 ``request.app.state.engine`` 访问引擎，并检查 ``None`` 情况（引擎尚未初始化）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1330
msgid ""
"The :class:`~lmcache.v1.multiprocess.http_api_registry.HTTPAPIRegistry` "
"will pick the module up automatically at startup — no central "
"registration list to edit."
msgstr ""
":class:`~lmcache.v1.multiprocess.http_api_registry.HTTPAPIRegistry` "
"将在启动时自动加载模块 — 无需编辑中央注册列表。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1334
msgid ""
"If the route is generic enough to be shared with the vLLM-embedded API "
"server, add it under ``lmcache/v1/internal_api_server/common/`` instead. "
"It will be picked up on the MP side via ``common_api.py`` unless its "
"module name is listed in ``_MP_INCOMPATIBLE_MODULES`` there (reserved for"
" modules that require vLLM-specific ``app.state`` attributes; the list is"
" currently empty). A handler that lives under "
"``internal_api_server/vllm/`` can still be surfaced on the MP server by "
"adding a thin re-export shim under ``http_apis/`` (as ``version_api.py`` "
"does for the version endpoints)."
msgstr "如果路由足够通用，可以与嵌入式 vLLM API 服务器共享，请将其添加到 ``lmcache/v1/internal_api_server/common/`` 下。它将在 MP 端通过 ``common_api.py`` 被加载，除非其模块名称在 ``_MP_INCOMPATIBLE_MODULES`` 中列出（保留给需要 vLLM 特定 ``app.state`` 属性的模块；该列表目前为空）。位于 ``internal_api_server/vllm/`` 下的处理程序仍然可以通过在 ``http_apis/`` 下添加一个薄的重新导出适配器来在 MP 服务器上显示（如 ``version_api.py`` 对版本端点所做的那样）。"

#: ../../source/mp/http_api.rst:1344
msgid ""
"When adding a new endpoint, please also add a matching section to this "
"page documenting the endpoint's purpose, request/response schema, and an "
"example ``curl`` invocation."
msgstr "添加新端点时，请在此页面上添加一个匹配的部分，记录端点的目的、请求/响应架构以及一个示例 ``curl`` 调用。"

